{"arkId":"cl010185642","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010185642","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"tablette","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"tablette"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : Ach\u00e9m\u00e9nide : Darius I (-522 - -486)","currentLocation":"Sully, [AO] Salle 309 - Iran - L\u0027empire perse ach\u00e9m\u00e9nide : Pers\u00e9polis et Suse, Vitrine 4 Langues et \u00e9critures d\u0027empire ach\u00e9m\u00e9nide","room":"Salle 309, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 0","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":-522,"endYear":-486,"imprecision":"","text":"Ach\u00e9m\u00e9nide : Darius I","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"SB 13078","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"AS 9917 308","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"},{"value":"MDP XI 308","type":"Num\u00e9ro catalogue"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s orientales","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"D\u00e9cor : inscription ; empreinte de sceau ; roi (tenant) ; taureau (2, aile) ; Ahura-Mazda\r\nPr\u00e9cision sur l\u0027objet : Tablette administrative en \u00e9lamite portant l\u0027empreinte d\u0027un sceau de Darius Ier. L\u0027empreinte montre un personnage couronn\u00e9, v\u00eatu d\u0027une robe perse tenant de chaque c\u00f4t\u00e9 la corne d\u0027un taureau ail\u00e9. La sc\u00e8ne est encadr\u00e9e par des palmiers. Au-dessus de la sc\u00e8ne, disque ail\u00e9 de Ahura-Mazda","inscriptions":"\u00c9criture : \r ; cun\u00e9iforme\r ; Inscription : \r ; Le texte rapporte l\u0027enregistrement de rations d\u0027huile distribu\u00e9es \u0022au nom du roi\u0022 \u00e0 Suse et dans cinq villages alentours. La tablette, unique en son genre \u00e0 Suse, porte un sceau royal, connu \u00e0 Pers\u00e9polis et utilis\u00e9 uniquement pour sceller des textes administratifs concernant des paiements en nature effectu\u00e9s sur les provisions royales\r ; Langue : \r ; \u00e9lamite\r ; n\u00e9o-\u00e9lamite\r ; Nature du texte : \r ; texte \u00e9conomique administratif","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"3,8","displayDimension":"3,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"4,8","displayDimension":"4,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,5","displayDimension":"2,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":5,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argile\r\nTechnique : model\u00e9, incis\u00e9","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"1906-1908","placeOfDiscovery":"Suse","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Morgan, Jacques Jean Marie de","note":" (mission)","role":", Fouilleur\/Arch\u00e9ologue"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"partage apr\u00e8s fouilles","doubt":"","dates":[]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s orientales","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"partage apr\u00e8s fouilles"}],"denomination":[{"value":"tablette"}],"material":[{"value":"argile"}],"technic":[{"value":"incis\u00e9"},{"value":"model\u00e9"}],"description":[{"value":"taureau"},{"value":"Ahura-Mazda"},{"value":"aile"},{"value":"roi"},{"value":"tenant"},{"value":"2 = double"},{"value":"inscription"},{"value":"empreinte de sceau"}],"inscriptionLanguage":[{"value":"\u00e9lamite"},{"value":"n\u00e9o-\u00e9lamite"}],"place":[{"value":"Suse"}],"inscriptionType":[{"value":"texte \u00e9conomique administratif"}],"inscriptionWritingSystem":[{"value":"cun\u00e9iforme"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Regards sur la... Perse